  <h1>Need Help?</h1>
  <p>
    Find answers about using our gamified learning platform. This page is tailored for learners in rural communities looking for support and tips!
  </p>

  <h2>Quick Start Guide</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Creating your account:</strong> Tap <em>Sign Up</em> on the homepage and provide your phone number or email.</li>
    <li><strong>Joining a course:</strong> Browse the Course Library after login and click <em>Join</em>.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How Gamification Works</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <span style="color:#157115;font-weight:bold;">Points:</span> Complete lessons, quizzes, and challenges to earn points.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span style="color:#157115;font-weight:bold;">Badges:</span> Unlock special badges when you reach major milestones, or keep up a study streak.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span style="color:#157115;font-weight:bold;">Leaderboard:</span> See your rank among other learners and get motivated!
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>FAQ</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Forgot your password?</strong>
      Click <em>Forgot Password</em> on the login page to reset it using your phone or email.
    </li>
    <li><strong>Website not working?</strong>
      Check your internet connection. If problems persist, try reloading or contact our support.
    </li>
  </ul>

